Xepher is a WeeChat plugin for XMPP/Jabber protocol support.

Features include multi-user chat (MUC), Message Archive Management (MAM),
OMEMO and PGP encryption, service discovery, avatars, HTTP file upload,
message carbons, typing indicators, and MUC bookmarks.

After installation, load the plugin in WeeChat:

	/plugin load xmpp

WWW: https://github.com/ekollof/xepher